---
title: Cajun Salmon and Colcannon with peas and garlic butter sauce
description: Salmon coated in a blend of Cajun spices accompanies creamy kale colcannon and vibrant green peas in a simple yet delicious dish that makes for the perfect weeknight meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R20_W09_IE_IECF20071-2_Main_high-102df41b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6571b2e82db9273db6a47c66.pdf
